<div class="card block">
    <div class="card-content">
        <p class="title" id="bi_library">
            Business Intelligence Library
        </p>
        <div class="columns">
            <div class="column">
                <div class="content">
                    <div class="block">
                        ETL processes collect report metadata from various platforms and store it in a centrally located database.
                    </div>
                    <div class="block">
                        Additional documentation is added through a modern web UI. Reports and documentation is fully searchable. Content can easily be favorited, shared and more.
                    </div>
                    <div class="block">
                        In a word, Atlas BI Library makes managing your report library stress free.
                    </div>
                    <figure class="image">
                        {% image "./src/static/img/atlas-home.png", "atlas home page", "(min-width:600px) 50vw, 100vw" %}
                    </figure>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <div class="content">
                    <div class="block">
                        <h4 class="ml-3 mb-5 pb-5"
                            style="transform: rotate(-3deg);">need better governance over your report documentation?</h4>
                        <h4 class="ml-1 mt-5 pt-5"
                            style="transform: rotate(4deg);">want to make documentation available to users?</h4>
                        <h4 class="ml-5 mt-5 pt-5"
                            style="transform: rotate(-1deg);">want to track and manage what reports end users are using?</h4>
                        <h4 class="ml-3 mt-5 pt-5"
                            style="transform: rotate(4deg);">easily favorite and share reports with colleagues?</h4>
                        <h4 class="ml-2 mt-5 pt-5"
                            style="transform: rotate(-2deg);">organize reports into projects?</h4>
                        <h4 class="pl-5 ml-5 mt-5 pt-5 mb-5 pb-5"
                            style="transform: rotate(-4deg);">schedule recurring report maintenance?</h4>
                        <h4 class="ml-1 mt-5 pt-5" style="transform: rotate(3deg);">track unused reports?</h4>
                        <h4 class="ml-3 mt-5 pt-5"
                            style="transform: rotate(1deg);">define specific concept that end users can access?</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container is-hidden-touch">{% include "home/library_alternate_tools.njk" %}</div>
        <div class="hero-body hero-two">
            <div class="container">{% include "home/library_demo.njk" %}</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
